Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:05:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大澤賢治？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得他已經退居二線了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要得知寶貝女兒被捲了進去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.21,0:06:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也認識那個日本記者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會場內部狀況依然不明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大澤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大澤！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.61,0:06:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大澤！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.53,0:06:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是跟著他的那個小丫頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.36,0:06:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且她還是鐵之鬥爭代理人的重要朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.67,0:07:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是大澤賢治嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是「{\1c&H0000FF&}蛇{\r}」　大澤賢治的車被炸掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我提議將戒備級別提高到3
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若沒有抗病毒劑 就無法進行救援
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.16,0:07:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我申請執行第二套方案
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經別無他法了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:08:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在掌握人民解放軍的是方先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我接中國大使
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再磨蹭下去 我軍第七艦隊會填滿台灣海峽的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了嗎 卑鄙的恐怖分子們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們有什麼要求
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若不互相瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就解決不了任何問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我 你們為什麼要用UA病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這種活在謊言裡的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(726,670)\fs30}希望之地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會是那傢伙的Canaan嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大總統 您不冷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位次官差不多該發臭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就給您開足了冷氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於開口了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑賤的恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 我們沒時間增進感情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再過幾個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們身上的UA病毒就會發作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們送命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.24,0:09:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你優秀的部下們好像不喜歡這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們為尊貴的大總統準備了特別的死法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 您引以為豪的隱形轟炸機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩小時前已從關島起飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攜帶著兩千磅制導炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.69,0:09:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完了 一切都完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝各位一路順風
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 那點微不足道的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.47,0:10:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有足夠時間供你們回味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從前有個倒霉的傭兵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他接了兩次同樣的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.25,0:10:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把拿不穩槍的小姑娘調教成一方高手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多麼無聊的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更倒霉的還在後頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的學生被冠以同一個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是迦南的什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.43,0:10:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也叫迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然已經捨棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們無論在任何情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都不能向恐怖分子屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這才是美國總統高潔的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 我們的道路已經注定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們的名字將被永遠鐫刻在反恐豐碑上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准許轟炸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit02 this is AWACS thousand-eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are cleared to commit bombing 310.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Engage in 230. Visual is clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your weapon is free.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May god be with you, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit02 will go. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.14,0:11:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她會無法救你 無法阻止轟炸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,墜入無底深淵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是克服一切 再次擋在我的面前呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在看來 似乎是後者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾法魯多大人 到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掙扎到最後吧 兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩位？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大澤賢治被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,束手無策的白宮打算使用禁招
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡說 這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會引發戰爭的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:13:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中國政府也不是團結一致的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對上海派來說 這是個好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 一個個都瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個房間還能用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thousand-eye, Spirit02.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ETA target 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是很久沒用了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.05,0:13:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與NSA協同作戰時 對方擅自設置的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後就沒動過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不能當大件垃圾處理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然老了一代 但應該能行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧 瑪麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.15,0:13:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能和外界聯絡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:13:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 地下還有UA病毒感染者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,UA病毒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 轟炸機似乎正飛往這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總算接通了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼好辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.26,0:14:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來你已經搞清狀況了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 告訴我你現在的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有很多顯示器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主控制室 正好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這就連網過去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要入侵美軍的導航衛星群
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.74,0:14:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們很煩耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 會場裡還有人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能被捨棄了 正抽泣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.87,0:15:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點 來個high tension
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,high tension來囉！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.07,0:15:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾法魯多大人 梁琪大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要管她了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 是捨棄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ETA target 2 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經連上你那邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳送入侵衛星的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我讀出什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.01,0:16:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才你用手機使用的功能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GPS？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會盡量掃除障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但還沒能最終鎖定範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.65,0:16:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才起 我就完全聽不懂你的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算用電波干擾麻痺GPS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有慣性制導 誤差在30米以內
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要徹底變更目標
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 你想…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統閣下 是大澤賢治
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 他不是死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holly shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.21,0:17:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Locked on target and standing by, 20 miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.87,0:17:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God help us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.43,0:17:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bomb's away. At 35 secends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.55,0:17:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轟炸中止！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,投了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們投彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離命中還有近40秒時間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我趕上！
