Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs70\t(0,200,1,\fs45)\t(710,910,1,\fs1)}4
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs70\t(0,200,1,\fs45)\t(700,900,1,\fs1)}3
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs70\t(0,200,1,\fs45)\t(660,860,1,\fs1)}2
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs70\t(0,200,1,\fs45)\t(580,780,1,\fs1)}1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs70\t(0,200,1,\fs40)\t(840,1040,1,\fs1)}Impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.61,0:19:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大澤…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.62,0:19:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大澤！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.49,0:19:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.89,0:19:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧 振作點！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炸彈呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 既然我們還活著…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南迦南迦南！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:19:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我只是創造了契機
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然夠亂來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 我聽不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.76,0:20:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說 迦南你太偉大了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}打偏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臨近命中時 GPS制導裝置受到不明干擾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未能直接命中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,落在了距目標五十米處
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知該不該慶幸打偏一事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 不允許失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.43,0:20:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此 才要一擊必殺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.98,0:20:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓轟炸機撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.25,0:20:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit02 abort mission
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,RTB immediately. I repeat
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這可怕的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:21:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但做這種義工 對你有什麼好處？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.12,0:21:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了直面過去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,容我反問一句
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃避過去 一直逃避下去 就能得到真正的救贖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.82,0:21:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨你喜歡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不可能 姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.37,0:21:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這已經不是喜歡的問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.07,0:21:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛是… 愛是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法抑制的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.42,0:21:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太陽公公 風兒 氧氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.71,0:21:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還活著！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.98,0:21:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.36,0:21:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顏色… 看不到顏色了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:21:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.74,0:22:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不… 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.94,0:22:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正的顏色
